channel.title: [Solved] Problem with Ints or models? you tell me
channel.description: For some reason when i add certain models they turn out like this: [img]http://img244.imageshack.us/img244/5254/30934415ld5.png[/img] You can see that the model is there its just like mest up i guess. What is causing this? the model or the ints

item.title: [Solved] Problem with Ints or models? you tell me
item.dc:creator: @wolfs_goal wolfs goal
item.description:
@wolfs_goal wrote:

you need to do this.

go into [item.java]

search “public int body[]”

then at the end of that add the item id

this will allow the server to read the item is a platebody type
